title: Can't see my own club
body:
Hey! 
I've had a problem that I can't see my own club even though my friends see me in it. 
Club's name is Whale Oil Corporation© and the tag is WOC©. Can it be fixed?

replies.body: Your club may have been out of sync!  I booped it for, though.  Relog and let me know if everything is okay now!
